snippet.title: Amber Heard Audio LEAKED - Full Audio of Amber Heard RAGING at Johnny Depp #JusticeForJohnnyDepp
snippet.description: Leaked Audio of Amber Heard Making Johnny Depp Miserable.  Revealing audio showing the true character of Amber Heard yelling at Johnny Depp and not acknowledging any of her faults.  The audio shows that men are victim of abuse too.  Amber Heard belittles Johnny Depp and faults him for trying to walk and away and keep distance after she physically assaults him.  She expects him to commit and put up with her anger issues, physical abuse, and she is a miserable person to be in a relationship with.
